{
  "stem": "24242.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then, in evening--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the only way I could describe it, I guess, is bad news.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't know if a kid in my-- I knew one thing, though.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If the policeman is there, I have to run the opposite, have to hide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there is-- was no way out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you just have to sit it out, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think I understood the real-- the real fear, the real consequences if you get caught.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I guess instinctly, to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they did not give me out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the evening, came my brothers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from there and on, I was never left in this area, in this immediate our-- around our village.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If I was left, it was already farther away, like 10 or 20 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Never left with a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And those neighbors, obviously, were very nice people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were good people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "White Russians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They could very easily give me away to the-- to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if they would get caught that they hiding a Jew, their life and their farm isn't worth a nickel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They would get burned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Killed and burned, the entire family, for helping a Jewish kid or whoever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they actually put their life totally at stake.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a lot of those people, White Russian, did get hurt from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A lot of them got killed for helping out Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in our area, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From this area, they were helping us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you helped us, later on, we were together, like 1,200 Jews got together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a-- it's a town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mainly at those days-- this was the very first winter into the war-- mainly--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'41.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Winter of 1941.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mainly those were people on good terms, and not on bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
